{"id":105328,"type":6,"name":"Gang Related","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/86/0f/105328_ao9qQ.jpg","summary":"　　警察Ryan Lopez是洛杉矶反黑组里一颗冉冉上升的新星。但别人不知道的是，在Ryan当警察之前，他曾经发誓效忠洛杉矶的一个拉丁黑帮“落山鸡”（Los Angelicos）。当Ryan最好的朋友兼搭档被一个臭名昭著的黑帮分子无情杀害后，他立马跟反黑组另一位成员Cassius Green组队侦破此案。通过这场执法部门于黑帮的战争，该剧将深入探讨这样一个事实——坏人也会做好事，好人也有黑暗面。 Ryan的知识都是从道上学来的，而这些知识将成为他反黑的优势之一。而他对警局日益增长的衷心和其他反黑组成员对他的帮助将影响他的站队。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>黑白无间道</li><li><span>别名: </span>正邪之间</li><li><span>集数: </span>13</li><li><span>开始: </span>2014-05-22</li><li><span>类型: </span>犯罪</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>FOX</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.fox.com/gang-related/</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt2719784</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"eps":[{"id":404240,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404240","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404241,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404241","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404242,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404242","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404243,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404243","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404244,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404244","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404245,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404245","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404246,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404246","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404247,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/404247","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":404248,"url":"htt